Paper: hep-th/9603076

Date: 1996-03-12

Title: Comment on the ``$\theta$-term renormalization in the (2+1)-dimensional

$CP^{N-1}$ model with $\theta$ term''Authors: I.N. Kondrashuk (JINR, Dubna) and A.V. Kotikov (ENSLAPP, Annecy and

JINR, Dubna)Comments: 3 pages, LATEX

Journal-ref: Phys.Rev. D53 (1996) 2260-2261

It is found that the recently published first coefficient of nonzero$\beta$-function for the Chern-Simons term in the $1/N$ expansion of the$CP^{N-1}$ model is untrue numerically. The correct result is given. The mainconclusions of Park's paper are not changed.